{{Anthroposophy}}
{{noteTA
|1 = zh-cn:印度教; zh-hant:印度教; zh-sg:兴都教;
}}
'''人智學'''（英語：Anthroposophy；德語：Anthroposophie）是由[[神秘主義|神秘主義]]者[[鲁道夫·施泰纳|鲁道夫·施泰纳]]<ref>[https://www.britannica.com/topic/anthroposophy Anthroposophy] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208022011/https://www.britannica.com/topic/anthroposophy|date=2021-02-08}}, Encyclopedia Britannica online. "Anthroposophy, philosophy based on the premise that the human intellect has the ability to contact spiritual worlds. It was formulated by Rudolf Steiner (q.v.), an Austrian philosopher, scientist, and artist, who postulated the existence of a spiritual world comprehensible to pure thought but fully accessible only to the faculties of knowledge latent in all humans."</ref>在 20 世紀初創立的一種[[哲學|哲學]]，它假設存在一個[[客觀|客觀]]的、[[智力|智力]]上可理解的[[靈性|靈性]]世界，可供人類[[體驗|體驗]]。該學說的追隨者旨在透過一種獨立於[[感官|感官]]體驗的[[思維|思維]][[模式|模式]]進行靈性探索。<ref name="Essential">Robert McDermott, ''The Essential Steiner'', {{ISBN|0-06-065345-0}}, pp. 3–11, 392–5</ref><ref>[http://library.eb.com/eb/article-9007798 "Anthroposophy"] {{Wayback|url=http://library.eb.com/eb/article-9007798 |date=20210814081920 }}, Encyclopædia Britannica online, accessed 10/09/07</ref> 他們還旨在以一種可透過[[理性|理性]][[話語|話語]]驗證的方式表達他們的[[想法|想法]]，並在研究靈性世界時尋求與研究[[物理|物理]]世界的科學家所獲得的精確度和清晰度相當。

人智學起源於[[德國唯心主義|德國唯心主義]]和神秘主義哲學。<ref>Christian Clement (ed.), ''Rudolf Steiner: Schriften über Mystik, Mysterienwesen und Religionsgeschichte''.  Frommann-holzboog Verlag, Stuttgart-Bad Cannstatt, 2013. {{ISBN|978-3-7728-2635-1}}. p. xlii</ref> 施泰納選擇了人智學這個詞（來自 anthropo-，[[人類|人類]]，和 sophia，[[智慧|智慧]]）來強調他的哲學的[[人文主義|人文主義]]取向。<ref name="Essential">Robert McDermott, ''The Essential Steiner'', {{ISBN|0-06-065345-0}}, pp. 3–11, 392–5</ref><ref>Rudolf Steiner, ''Waldorf Education and Anthroposophy'', Anthroposophic Press 1995 {{ISBN|0880103876}}</ref> 他將其定義為“對靈性世界的[[科學|科學]]探索”<ref>{{Cite book|last=Steiner|first=Rudolf|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=jNAOAAAAIAAJ&q=Philosophie+und+Anthroposophie,++Rudolf+Steiner|title=Philosophie und Anthroposophie: Gesammelte Aufsätze, 1904-1918|date=1965|publisher=Verlag der Rudolf Steiner-Nachlassverwaltung|language=de|access-date=2021-12-22|archive-date=2021-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211222121546/https://books.google.com/books?id=jNAOAAAAIAAJ&q=Philosophie+und+Anthroposophie,++Rudolf+Steiner|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其他人又稱其為“[[哲學|哲學]]和[[文化|文化]]運動”<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/794328527|title=Handbook of new religions and cultural production|date=2012|publisher=BRILL|others=Carole M. Cusack, Alex Norman|isbn=978-90-04-22648-7|location=Leiden|oclc=794328527|access-date=2021-02-17|archive-date=2021-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210601024953/https://www.worldcat.org/title/handbook-of-new-religions-and-cultural-production/oclc/794328527|url-status=live}}</ref>、“靈性運動”<ref>{{Cite book|last=Phillips|first=D. C.|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=84StBAAAQBAJ&q=phillips+encyclopedia+of+educational+theory+and+philosophy|title=Encyclopedia of Educational Theory and Philosophy|date=2014-05-19|publisher=SAGE Publications|isbn=978-1-4833-6475-9|pages=847|language=en|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210601024947/https://books.google.com/books?id=84StBAAAQBAJ&q=phillips+encyclopedia+of+educational+theory+and+philosophy|url-status=live}}</ref>、“靈性科學”<ref>{{Cite book|last=Steiner|first=Rudolf|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/49531507|title=What is anthroposophy? : three perspectives on self-knowledge|date=2002|publisher=Anthroposophic Press|others=Christopher Bamford|isbn=0-88010-506-2|location=Great Barrington, MA|oclc=49531507|access-date=2021-02-17|archive-date=2021-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210601024956/https://www.worldcat.org/title/what-is-anthroposophy-three-perspectives-on-self-knowledge/oclc/49531507|url-status=live}}</ref>或“一個[[思想體系|思想體系]]”（英語：a system of thought）<ref>{{Cite book|last1=Weiner|first1=Irving B.|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=be0VYic5iWwC&q=Corsini%20encyclopedia%20of%20psychology|title=The Corsini Encyclopedia of Psychology, Volume 1|last2=Craighead|first2=W. Edward|date=2010-01-19|publisher=John Wiley & Sons|isbn=978-0-470-17025-0|pages=86|language=en|access-date=2021-04-10|archive-date=2021-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210601024948/https://books.google.com/books?id=be0VYic5iWwC&q=Corsini+encyclopedia+of+psychology|url-status=live}}</ref>等。人智學思想已被用於許多領域的替代運動，包括教育（在[[華德福學校|華德福學校]]和坎普希爾運動（英語：Camphill Movement）中）、農業（[[生物動力農法|生物動力農法]]）、醫學、銀行、[[組織發展理論|組織發展]]和藝術。<ref name="Essential">Robert McDermott, ''The Essential Steiner'', {{ISBN|0-06-065345-0}}, pp. 3–11, 392–5</ref><ref name="Willmann">Carlo Willmann, ''Waldorfpädagogik: Theologische und religionspädagogische Befunde'', {{ISBN|3-412-16700-2}}, Chap. 1</ref><ref>[http://www.ibe.unesco.org/publications/ThinkersPdf/steinere.pdf Heiner Ullrich, "Rudolf Steiner"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924041958/http://www.ibe.unesco.org/publications/ThinkersPdf/steinere.pdf|date=2015-09-24}}, ''Prospects: the quarterly review of comparative education'' (Paris, UNESCO: International Bureau of Education), vol. XXIV, no. 3/4, 1994, p. 555–572.</ref><ref name="Schneider">Peter Schneider, Einführung in die Waldorfpädogogik, {{ISBN|3-608-93006-X}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Ullrich|first=Heiner|title=Rudolf Steiner: Leben und Lehre|year=2010|publisher=C. H. Beck|location=Munich|page=9}}</ref> 

然而，許多[[科學家|科學家]]和醫師等批評了人智學的應用在醫學、生物學、農業和教育領域是危險的和[[偽科學|偽科學]]的。<ref>{{cite book|title=The Skeptic Encyclopedia of Pseudoscience|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Gr4snwg7iaEC&pg=PA33|publisher=ABC-CLIO|isbn=9781576076538|pages=31–|year=2002|access-date=2016-10-17|archive-date=2016-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161224093537/https://books.google.com/books?id=Gr4snwg7iaEC&pg=PA33|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="Ruse2013">{{cite book|last=Ruse|first=Michael|title=The Gaia Hypothesis: Science on a Pagan Planet|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=EQRuAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA128|access-date=21 June 2015|date=2013-09-25|publisher=University of Chicago Press|isbn=9780226060392|pages=128–}}</ref><ref name="GuardianWaldorf">{{cite news|title=Schools of pseudoscience pose a serious threat to education {{!}} letters|url=https://www.theguardian.com/theobserver/2012/may/13/letters-steiner-maharishi-schools-wrong|access-date=29 November 2018|work=The Guardian|date=12 May 2012|language=en|archive-date=10 September 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170910173601/https://www.theguardian.com/theobserver/2012/may/13/letters-steiner-maharishi-schools-wrong|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="Gorski">{{cite web|title=A University of Michigan Medical School alumnus confronts anthroposophic medicine at his alma mater|url=https://sciencebasedmedicine.org/a-university-of-michigan-medical-school-alumnus-confronts-anthroposophic-medicine-at-his-alma-mater/|access-date=29 November 2018|date=14 March 2011|website=Science-Based Medicine|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507155634/https://sciencebasedmedicine.org/a-university-of-michigan-medical-school-alumnus-confronts-anthroposophic-medicine-at-his-alma-mater/|archive-date=7 May 2019|last1=Gorski|first1=David|url-status=live}}</ref> 斯坦納的一些觀點偏離了[[科学史|現代科學]]，包括：“種族”進化（參見[[社會達爾文主義|社會達爾文主義]]與[[種族主義|種族主義]]）<ref name="StaudenmaierRace">{{cite journal|title=Race and Redemption: Racial and Ethnic Evolution in Rudolf Steiner's Anthroposophy|first1=Peter|date=1 February 2008|journal=Nova Religio|issue=3|doi=10.1525/nr.2008.11.3.4|volume=11|pages=4–36|last1=Staudenmaier|access-date=}}</ref><ref name="Staudenmaier">{{cite web|title=Between Occultism and Fascism: Anthroposophy and the Politics of Race and Nation in Germany and Italy, 1900-1945|url=https://ecommons.cornell.edu/bitstream/handle/1813/17662/Staudenmaier%2C%20Peter.pdf|access-date=5 September 2021|publisher=Cornell University|last1=Staudenmaier|first1=Peter|archive-date=2021-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210818150945/https://ecommons.cornell.edu/bitstream/handle/1813/17662/Staudenmaier,%20Peter.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>、「[[透視_(超感官知覺)|透視]]」（或作靈視，斯坦納聲稱自己有該方面的能力）<ref name="QuackWatch">{{cite web|title=Rudolf Steiner's Quackery|url=https://quackwatch.org/11ind/steiner/|access-date=5 September 2021|date=23 July 2012|publisher=Quackwatch|last1=Kreidler|first1=Marc|archive-date=2019-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190323012309/https://www.quackwatch.org/11Ind/steiner.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[亞特蘭蒂斯|亞特蘭蒂斯]]的神話<ref name="StaudenmaierRace2">{{cite journal|title=Race and Redemption: Racial and Ethnic Evolution in Rudolf Steiner's Anthroposophy|first1=Peter|date=1 February 2008|journal=Nova Religio|issue=3|doi=10.1525/nr.2008.11.3.4|volume=11|pages=4–36|last1=Staudenmaier|access-date=}}</ref>。

